<h2>AI Doctor - Complete AI Powered Healthcare / Doctor Practice Management System</h2>

<p><strong>AI Doctor</strong> is a comprehensive, modern healthcare practice management system powered by cutting-edge artificial intelligence. Built with Next.js 15, React 19, and TypeScript, this system combines traditional practice management features with advanced AI capabilities to help healthcare professionals provide better patient care and streamline their operations.</p>

